      "id": "PopularPost8110",
      "post_content": "2/5. It seems solid, but really you want this kind of effect at instant speed. And most would rather kill the creature than just reduce its power by 2. That means [Nameless Inversino](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nameless Inversino) is clearly superior...as is something like [Terror](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror) (except, obviously, against black and/or artifact decks). There is really no reason for effects like this to be auras in the first place though...instant (but until end of turn) effects are much nicer for black, who should want to deal with these threats immediately, suddenly and unexpectedly.",
      "posted_by": "kitsunewarlock",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost8110\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">2/5.  It seems solid, but really you want this kind of effect at instant speed.  And most would rather kill the creature than just reduce its power by 2.  That means <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Nameless Inversino\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nameless Inversino\">Nameless Inversino</a> is clearly superior...as is something like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Terror\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror\">Terror</a> (except, obviously, against black and/or artifact decks).  There is really no reason for effects like this to be auras in the first place though...instant (but until end of turn) effects are much nicer for black, who should want to deal with these threats immediately, suddenly and unexpectedly.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '8110'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy486\">kitsunewarlock</span>\r\n                                (6/2/2009 1:22:20 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRat